				\begin{document}$${\alpha }_{sc}=\frac{{P}_{sc,V}}{2{P}_{0,A}}$$\end{document}αsc=Psc,V2P0,Aand the total amplitude attenuation is obtained by combining with the attenuation in bulk water12\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
